cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about video object segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new framework that integrates object detection, segmentation, and re-identification, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category as well. The paper also discusses the efficiency and speed of the proposed method, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper mentions the potential application of the proposed method in robotics, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics).
